### User & Organizer Profile Testing

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api
@userToken = YOUR_USER_ACCESS_TOKEN
@orgToken = YOUR_ORG_ACCESS_TOKEN
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN

### 1. [USER] Get My User Profile
# Requires: Any authenticated user token
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles/me
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 2. [USER] Update My User Profile
# Requires: Any authenticated user token
PUT {{baseUrl}}/profiles/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
    "fullName": "John Doe",
    "language": "am"
}

### 3. [ORGANIZER] Get My Organizer Profile
# Requires: Role ORGANIZER or ADMIN
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles/organizer
Authorization: Bearer {{orgToken}}

### 4. [ORGANIZER] Update My Organizer Profile
# Requires: Role ORGANIZER
PUT {{baseUrl}}/profiles/organizer
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{orgToken}}

{
    "organizationName": "Doe Events Ltd",
    "city": "Addis Ababa",
    "payoutDetails": "CBE: 1000123456789",
    "contactEmail": "contact@doeevents.com"
}

### 5. [ADMIN] List All Organizer Applications
# Requires: Role ADMIN
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles/admin/organizers
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6. [ADMIN] Review/Approve Organizer
# Requires: Role ADMIN
# Replace :id with the OrganizerProfile ID from Request #5
# status can be: APPROVED or REJECTED
POST {{baseUrl}}/profiles/admin/organizers/1/review
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "status": "APPROVED",
    "adminNote": "Business license verified."
}
